\pard\f0\fs28   It is not certain whether this species occurs frequently in Europe, and many records clearly refer to {\b 24}. The European plants referred to this species differ somewhat from those from Anatolia, and are transitional to {\b 24}. Their taxonomic position must be considered uncertain.
